{{see|Giant}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Via Middle English from Old French, ultimately from Latin ''[[gigas]]''; compare French ''[[géant]]''

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪənt|-aɪənt]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[mythical]] human of very great size.
# A very tall person.
# An [[ethernet]] [[packet]] that exceeds the medium's maximum packet size of 1,518 [[bytes]].

